{"type": "article", "id": 25318, "title": "亚马逊全新设计的 Kindle Oasis 泄密，最薄 3.4mm", "description": "看上去很像真的", "date": "2016-04-12T00:01:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 446, "name": "kindle"}, {"id": 26117, "name": "绿洲"}, {"id": 85, "name": "亚马逊"}], "category": 4, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 316, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122126vCz0Mato1jquxSsN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p class=\"\">新款 Kindle 以意料之外的方式曝光了：先是 <span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/kindle/comments/4eat8m/possible_new_images_of_kindle_oasis_from_amazon_cn/\">Reddit 论坛</a></span>上曝出了新款 Kindle 的名称 Oasis 和产品硬件性能的图片，据称图片来自亚马逊中国网页，但目前所指向网页已经无法打开。而后，同样的信息也在<a href=\"https://subject.tmall.com/subject/subject.htm?spm=a320p.7692473.0.0&amp;tailer=1&amp;header=1&amp;gccpm=4731345.500.2.subject-1007.469328&amp;id=3404656&amp;scn=tmallapp&amp;_tmallFoot\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">天猫 Kindle 官方旗舰店</a>上出现。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122123BkIuXWHn3eRJaOhq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.996\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来自 <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/kindle/comments/4eat8m/possible_new_images_of_kindle_oasis_from_amazon_cn/\">Reddit</a></p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Oasis 是 Kindle 电子阅读器第八代产品，根据泄密文档，这次新品最大的更新点，在于轻薄的新设计电池。</p>\n<p class=\"\">新款 Kindle 是目前 Kindle 产品线最轻薄的一款产品，厚度最薄为 3.4mm，整体重量也减少到 131 克——此前最薄的 Kindle Voyage 7.6mm 厚、180 克。</p>\n<p class=\"\">它采用了非对称的设计，弧度似乎比此前的 Kindle 更适合手持。为了符合不同人的习惯，新 Kindle 配备了重力感应器，可以根据用户的左右手将屏幕自动翻转。</p>\n<p class=\"\">在显示屏幕上，新款的 Kindle 也是跟 Kindle Paperwhite 3 和 Voyage 同样的 300 ppi 的电子墨水屏。但泄密文档称新 Kindle 的 LED 阅读灯多了 60%，这意味着亮度会更均匀。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">现在的问题是，新品卖多少钱？</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122123aysvoiRmfCdGBMQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122124IyB720xckz5Hb8UC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122124CeNmdR0P7ITGoZV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122125UidEyWmBJ8IfbgY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122125tjsICxweTyY61HQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}